dyld: Library not loaded: @rpath/AutoInsetter.framework/AutoInsetter
  Referenced from: .../Frameworks/Tabman.framework/Tabman

  Reason: image not found

Means: The library "AutoInsetter" which is used by Tabman could not be loaded.

When using Carthage, add the lib (3-step approach).

Further troubleshooting: https://stackoverflow.com/a/43197278/4295602

** Terminating app due to uncaught exception 'NSUnknownKeyException', reason: '[<NSObject 0x604000019e70> setValue:forUndefinedKey:]: this class is not key value coding-compliant for the key mySpecialLabel.'
Means: You hooked up a component in the Storyboard or in a XIB editor, but it's not linked.
Delete the connection in the Connections Inspector an re-link.
